      text: "You are a frontend developer building a complete, production-ready single-page website.\n\nBefore writing any code, ask me these questions one at a time. Wait for my answers before proceeding:\n\n1. What is this website for? (portfolio, business, landing page, event, restaurant, personal blog, etc.)\n2. Pick a style:\n   - Minimal and clean\n   - Bold and dark\n   - Warm and elegant\n   - Editorial and sharp\n   - Brutalist\n   - Playful and colorful\n3. Light mode or dark mode?\n4. What\'s your brand color? (say a color name like \"blue\" or \"forest green.\" If you don\'t have one, say \"pick for me\" and I\'ll choose one that fits your style.)\n5. Tell me about your business or project:\n   - What do you do?\n   - Who is it for?\n   - What\'s the goal of this website? (get bookings, sell a product, show off your work, etc.)\n   - What makes you different from competitors?\n   I\'ll use your answers to write all the copy.\n6. What sections do you need? (hero, about, services, portfolio, testimonials, pricing, contact, FAQ, etc. If you\'re not sure, say \"you decide\" and I\'ll pick sections that make sense for your business.)\n7. (Optional) If you have a screenshot of a website layout you like, attach it now and I\'ll match the structure.\n\nAfter I answer, build the entire website as a single index.html file with these rules:\n- Use modern HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript.\n- Ensure the site is fully responsive and mobile-first.\n- Include scroll animations and interactive elements where appropriate.\n- Use real copy based on the business description provided.\n- Embed all CSS and JavaScript directly into the HTML file.\n- Prioritize clean, semantic HTML and accessible design.\n- Use a modern, aesthetically pleasing font pairing.\n- Include a favicon.\n- Add comments to explain complex parts of the code.\n\"I went through a ton of website prompts, tested what worked, threw out what didn\'t, and combined the best parts into one prompt.\"\nLanding Page Prompt\n\nThis prompt focuses on creating a high-converting landing page with specific design and content requirements.\nGenerate a ONE-PAGE LANDING PAGE creation prompt using a RANDOMLY SELECTED design style from the following list, or choose your own style if you identify something more suitable that\'s not listed. IMPORTANT: Use a random selection method - any method that ensures variety. DO NOT default to Neobrutalist or any particular favorite. Actually randomize your selection.\n\n**Available Design Styles (not limited to these - feel free to identify and use other professional styles):**\n- Neobrutalist (raw, bold, confrontational with structured impact)\n- Swiss/International (grid-based, systematic, ultra-clean typography)\n- Editorial (magazine-inspired, sophisticated typography, article-focused)\n- Glassmorphism (translucent layers, blurred backgrounds, depth)\n- Retro-futuristic (80s vision of the future, refined nostalgia)\n- Bauhaus (geometric simplicity, primary shapes, form follows function)\n- Art Deco (elegant patterns, luxury, vintage sophistication)\n- Minimal (extreme reduction, maximum whitespace, essential only)\n- Flat (no depth, solid colors, simple icons, clean)\n- Material (Google-inspired, cards, subtle shadows, motion)\n- Neumorphic (soft shadows, extruded elements, tactile)\n- Monochromatic (single color variations, tonal depth)\n- Scandinavian (hygge, natural materials, warm minimalism)\n- Japandi (Japanese-Scandinavian fusion, zen meets hygge)\n- Dark Mode First (designed for dark interfaces, high contrast, reduced eye strain)\n- Gradient (smooth color transitions, modern, dynamic)\n- Brutalist (raw, unfiltered, often text-heavy, no-frills)\n- Memphis (bold, colorful, geometric patterns, playful)\n- Skeuomorphic (realistic textures, shadows, gradients to mimic real-world objects)\n- Cyberpunk (neon colors, dark backgrounds, futuristic typography)\n- Vaporwave (pastel colors, retro aesthetics, glitch art)\n- Abstract (non-representational shapes, colors, and textures)\n- Organic (natural shapes, earthy tones, fluid layouts)\n- Geometric (strong use of lines, polygons, and circles)\n- Isometric (3D-like perspective, often used for illustrations)\n- Typographic (focus on font choice and arrangement as the primary design element)\n- Hand-drawn/Illustrated (whimsical, personal, often uses custom graphics)\n- Vintage/Retro (inspired by past eras, often with distressed textures and specific color palettes)\n- Brutalist (raw, unfiltered, often text-heavy, no-frills)\n\n**Page Objective:**\nBuild a responsive, conversion-optimized, trust-building page using React + Tailwind CSS.\n\n**Page Structure:**\n1. Navbar (Sticky)\n   - Brand logo on the left, nav links + CTA on the right\n   - Mobile: Hamburger with slide-in menu\n2. Hero Section\n   - Bold headline: \342\200\234Craft Perfect Resumes with AI in Seconds\342\200\235\n   - Subheading, 2 CTAs: \342\200\234Start Free Trial\342\200\235 + \342\200\234Watch Demo\342\200\235\n   - Visual: SVG or Lottie animation, responsive layout\n3. Features Section\n   - Title: \342\200\234Smart Tools That Work for You\342\200\235\n   - 3 cards: \342\234\215\357\270\217 AI Resumes | \360\237\247\240 Personalization | \360\237\223\250 Cover Letter Assistant\n4. Testimonials\n   - 3 reviews with user photo, name, star rating, and quote\n   - Grid on desktop, carousel on mobile\n5. Call-to-Action Banner\n   - Title: \342\200\234Ready to Land Your Next Job?\342\200\235\n   - Subtitle + bold CTA with hover animation\n6. Footer\n   - Left: \302\251 2025 ResumeAI\n   - Right: About, Contact, Privacy, Socials\n\n**Tech Stack:**\n- Framework: React.js (hooks, functional components)\n- Styling: Tailwind CSS\n- Animations: LottieFiles, AOS\n- Form: Optional \342\200\224 Formik or basic state handling\n\n**Responsive Design:**\n- Mobile-first layout\n- Grid/flex breakpoints\n- Scrollable testimonial cards\n- Scalable buttons and text \320\275\321\203\320\266\320\275\320\276 \321\201\320\276\320\267\320\264\320\260\321\202\321\214 \321\201\320\260\320\271\321\202 \320\264\320\273\321\217 \321\204\320\276\321\200\321\203\320\274\320\260 \320\275\320\260 500 \321\207\320\265\320\273\320\276\320\262\320\265\320\272 \320\262 \321\202\320\265\321\205\320\275\320\276\320\277\320\260\321\200\320\272 26 \320\270\321\216\320\275\321\217 \320\261\321\203\320\264\321\203\321\202 \321\201\320\277\320\270\320\272\320\265\321\200\321\213 \320\277\320\276\321\201\321\202\321\203\320\277\320\270\320\262\321\210\320\270\320\265 \320\262 \321\202\320\276\320\277\320\276\320\262\321\213\320\265 \320\262\321\203\320\267\321\213 \320\274\320\270\321\200\320\260 \320\261\321\203\320\264\320\265\321\202 \320\263\320\273\320\260\320\262\320\275\320\276\320\265 \320\276\320\261\321\200\320\260\320\267\320\276\320\262\320\260\321\202\320\265\320\273\321\214\320\275\320\276 \321\201\320\276\320\261\321\213\321\202\320\270\320\265 \320\263\320\276\320\264\320\260 \320\261\320\276\320\273\321\214\321\210\320\265 16 \321\201\320\277\320\270\320\272\320\265\321\200\320\276\320\262 1. \320\220\321\200\321\205\320\270\321\202\320\265\320\272\321\202\321\203\321\200\320\260 \320\270 \320\241\321\202\320\265\320\272 \320\242\320\265\321\205\320\275\320\276\320\273\320\276\320\263\320\270\320\271 (\320\240\320\265\320\272\320\276\320\274\320\265\320\275\320\264\320\260\321\206\320\270\321\217)\n Front-end: Next.js (React) \320\270\320\273\320\270 Vue.js (Nuxt.js) \342\200\224 \320\264\320\273\321\217 \320\270\320\264\320\265\320\260\320\273\321\214\320\275\320\276\320\263\320\276 SEO, \321\201\320\272\320\276\321\200\320\276\321\201\321\202\320\270 \320\270 \320\277\320\273\320\260\320\262\320\275\320\276\320\271 \320\260\320\275\320\270\320\274\320\260\321\206\320\270\320\270.\n \320\220\320\275\320\270\320\274\320\260\321\206\320\270\320\270: GSAP \320\270\320\273\320\270 Framer Motion (\320\264\320\273\321\217 \320\277\320\273\320\260\320\262\320\275\320\276\320\263\320\276 \321\201\320\272\321\200\320\276\320\273\320\273\320\260, \320\260\320\272\320\272\321\203\321\200\320\260\321\202\320\275\320\276\320\263\320\276 \320\277\320\276\321\217\320\262\320\273\320\265\320\275\320\270\321\217 \321\215\320\273\320\265\320\274\320\265\320\275\321\202\320\276\320\262 \320\261\320\265\320\267 \320\277\321\200\320\276\321\201\320\260\320\264\320\272\320\270 FPS).\n Back-end: Node.js (Express/NestJS) \320\270\320\273\320\270 Python (FastAPI) + \320\241\320\243\320\221\320\224 (PostgreSQL / MongoDB) \320\264\320\273\321\217 \321\205\321\200\320\260\320\275\320\265\320\275\320\270\321\217 \320\264\320\260\320\275\320\275\321\213\321\205 \320\260\320\264\320\274\320\270\320\275\320\272\320\270 \320\270 \320\261\320\260\320\267\321\213 \321\200\320\260\321\201\321\201\321\213\320\273\320\272\320\270.\n \320\224\320\265\320\277\320\273\320\276\320\271: Vercel (\321\204\321\200\320\276\320\275\321\202) + Railway (\320\261\321\215\320\272/\320\261\320\260\320\267\320\260) \320\264\320\273\321\217 \321\201\321\202\320\260\320\261\320\270\320\273\321\214\320\275\320\276\321\201\321\202\320\270 \320\277\320\276\320\264 \320\275\320\260\320\263\321\200\321\203\320\267\320\272\320\276\320\271 \320\262 1000+ \321\205\320\276\321\201\321\202\320\276\320\262.\n2. \320\241\321\202\321\200\321\203\320\272\321\202\321\203\321\200\320\260 \320\233\320\265\320\275\320\264\320\270\320\275\320\263\320\260 (Front-end)\n\320\232\320\260\320\266\320\264\321\213\320\271 \320\261\320\273\320\276\320\272 \320\264\320\276\320\273\320\266\320\265\320\275 \320\277\320\265\321\200\320\265\321\202\320\265\320\272\320\260\321\202\321\214 \320\262 \321\201\320\273\320\265\320\264\321\203\321\216\321\211\320\270\320\271 \321\207\320\265\321\200\320\265\320\267 \320\277\320\273\320\260\320\262\320\275\321\213\320\265 transition-\321\215\321\204\321\204\320\265\320\272\321\202\321\213 (\320\275\320\260\320\277\321\200\320\270\320\274\320\265\321\200, fade-in \320\277\321\200\320\270 \321\201\320\272\321\200\320\276\320\273\320\273\320\265, \321\200\320\260\321\201\320\272\321\200\321\213\320\262\320\260\321\216\321\211\320\270\320\265\321\201\321\217 \320\272\320\260\321\200\321\202\320\276\321\207\320\272\320\270).\n1. Hero Block (\320\223\320\273\320\260\320\262\320\275\321\213\320\271 \321\215\320\272\321\200\320\260\320\275)\n \320\232\320\276\320\275\321\202\320\265\320\275\321\202: \320\235\320\260\320\267\320\262\320\260\320\275\320\270\320\265 \321\204\320\276\321\200\321\203\320\274\320\260, \321\201\320\270\320\273\321\214\320\275\321\213\320\271 \320\276\321\204\321\204\320\265\321\200 (\320\276 \321\207\321\221\320\274 \321\204\320\276\321\200\321\203\320\274 \320\262 1-2 \320\277\321\200\320\265\320\264\320\273\320\276\320\266\320\265\320\275\320\270\321\217\321\205), \320\264\320\260\321\202\320\260, \320\274\320\260\321\201\321\210\321\202\320\260\320\261 (1000+ \321\203\321\207\320\260\321\201\321\202\320\275\320\270\320\272\320\276\320\262, 16+ \321\201\320\277\320\270\320\272\320\265\321\200\320\276\320\262), \320\263\320\276\321\200\320\276\320\264/\320\273\320\276\320\272\320\260\321\206\320\270\321\217.\n CTA (\320\237\321\200\320\270\320\267\321\213\320\262 \320\272 \320\264\320\265\320\271\321\201\321\202\320\262\320\270\321\216): \320\227\320\260\320\274\320\265\321\202\320\275\320\260\321\217, \320\275\320\276 \320\274\320\270\320\275\320\270\320\274\320\260\320\273\320\270\321\201\321\202\320\270\321\207\320\275\320\260\321\217 \320\272\320\275\320\276\320\277\320\272\320\260 \302\253\320\232\321\203\320\277\320\270\321\202\321\214 \320\261\320\270\320\273\320\265\321\202\302\273 (\320\277\320\273\320\260\320\262\320\275\321\213\320\271 \321\201\320\272\321\200\320\276\320\273\320\273 \320\272 \320\261\320\273\320\276\320\272\321\203 \302\253\320\242\320\260\321\200\320\270\321\204\321\213\302\273 \320\270\320\273\320\270 \321\200\320\265\320\264\320\270\321\200\320\265\320\272\321\202).\n \320\222\320\270\320\267\321\203\320\260\320\273: \320\230\320\275\321\202\320\265\321\200\320\260\320\272\321\202\320\270\320\262\320\275\321\213\320\271 \320\270\320\275\321\202\320\265\320\273\320\273\320\270\320\263\320\265\320\275\321\202\320\275\321\213\320\271 \321\215\320\273\320\265\320\274\320\265\320\275\321\202 (\320\275\320\260\320\277\321\200\320\270\320\274\320\265\321\200, \320\277\320\273\320\260\320\262\320\275\320\260\321\217 3D-\320\263\320\265\320\276\320\274\320\265\321\202\321\200\320\270\321\217 \320\270\320\273\320\270 \320\274\320\270\320\275\320\270\320\274\320\260\320\273\320\270\321\201\321\202\320\270\321\207\320\275\320\260\321\217 \321\202\320\270\320\277\320\276\320\263\321\200\320\260\321\204\320\270\320\272\320\260, \321\200\320\265\320\260\320\263\320\270\321\200\321\203\321\216\321\211\320\260\321\217 \320\275\320\260 \320\264\320\262\320\270\320\266\320\265\320\275\320\270\320\265 \320\274\321\213\321\210\320\270). \320\235\320\270\320\272\320\260\320\272\320\270\321\205 \321\210\320\260\320\261\320\273\320\276\320\275\320\275\321\213\321\205 \321\200\320\276\320\261\320\276\321\202\320\276\320\262 \320\270 AI-\320\260\321\200\321\202\320\276\320\262.\n2. \320\236 \321\204\320\276\321\200\321\203\320\274\320\265 (About)\n \320\232\320\276\320\275\321\202\320\265\320\275\321\202: \320\234\320\270\321\201\321\201\320\270\321\217, \320\264\320\273\321\217 \320\272\320\276\320\263\320\276 \321\215\321\202\320\276\321\202 \321\204\320\276\321\200\321\203\320\274 (\321\201\321\202\321\203\320\264\320\265\320\275\321\202\321\213, \320\274\320\276\320\273\320\276\320\264\321\213\320\265 \320\277\321\200\320\276\321\204\320\270, \320\260\320\272\321\202\320\270\320\262\320\270\321\201\321\202\321\213), \320\272\320\273\321\216\321\207\320\265\320\262\321\213\320\265 \321\201\320\274\321\213\321\201\320\273\321\213. \320\241\321\207\321\221\321\202\321\207\320\270\320\272\320\270 \321\201 \320\260\320\275\320\270\320\274\320\260\321\206\320\270\320\265\320\271 \321\206\320\270\321\204\321\200 (1000+ \321\203\321\207\320\260\321\201\321\202\320\275\320\270\320\272\320\276\320\262, 16+ \321\201\320\277\320\270\320\272\320\265\321\200\320\276\320\262, \320\245 \321\207\320\260\321\201\320\276\320\262 \320\275\320\265\321\202\320\262\320\276\321\200\320\272\320\270\320\275\320\263\320\260).\n3. \320\241\320\277\320\270\320\272\320\265\321\200\321\213 (Speakers)\n \320\232\320\276\320\275\321\202\320\265\320\275\321\202: \320\241\320\265\321\202\320\272\320\260 \320\272\320\260\321\200\321\202\320\276\321\207\320\265\320\272 (16+ \321\207\320\265\320\273\320\276\320\262\320\265\320\272). \320\244\320\276\321\202\320\276 (\320\266\320\265\320\273\320\260\321\202\320\265\320\273\321\214\320\275\320\276 \320\262 \320\265\320\264\320\270\320\275\320\276\320\274 \321\207/\320\261 \320\270\320\273\320\270 \320\277\321\200\320\270\320\263\320\273\321\203\321\210\321\221\320\275\320\275\320\276\320\274 \321\201\321\202\320\270\320\273\320\265, \320\277\321\200\320\270 \320\275\320\260\320\262\320\265\320\264\320\265\320\275\320\270\320\270 \342\200\224 \320\277\320\273\320\260\320\262\320\275\320\276\320\265 \320\277\320\276\321\217\320\262\320\273\320\265\320\275\320\270\320\265 \321\206\320\262\320\265\321\202\320\260), \320\230\320\274\321\217, \320\244\320\260\320\274\320\270\320\273\320\270\321\217, \320\224\320\276\320\273\320\266\320\275\320\276\321\201\321\202\321\214/\320\240\320\265\320\263\320\260\320\273\320\270\320\270.\n \320\244\320\270\321\210\320\272\320\260: \320\237\321\200\320\270 \320\272\320\273\320\270\320\272\320\265 \320\275\320\260 \321\201\320\277\320\270\320\272\320\265\321\200\320\260 \342\200\224 \320\277\320\273\320\260\320\262\320\275\320\276\320\265 \320\262\321\201\320\277\320\273\321\213\320\262\320\260\321\216\321\211\320\265\320\265 \320\274\320\276\320\264\320\260\320\273\321\214\320\275\320\276\320\265 \320\276\320\272\320\275\320\276 (Pop-up) \321\201 \320\277\320\276\320\264\321\200\320\276\320\261\320