  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Achieving Perfection Today**\n\nI\'m incredibly pleased to report we\'ve nailed the website design! The \"Light/Airy Minimalism\" aesthetic is spot-on for \"The Main Educational Event of the Year\". I\'m also thrilled with the quality of our content - 17+ admissions experts from top universities, plus complete Kazakhstan references (Astana, Almaty). Success has been fully achieved.\n\n\n**Building the Admin Panel**\n\nI\'ve just finished a secure Administrative Board. It\'s a robust CMS panel with full CRUD operations. Speakers, timelines, partnerships, descriptions, and passwords are all fully editable. I\'ve also incorporated telemetry, subscriber databases, and an email export function. The administrative view has been fully enabled.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have successfully designed, built, and compiled the landing page and administration control console for **\"The Main Educational Event of the Year\"**! \n\nThe application is engineered as a **full-stack React-Vite-Express workspace** running on Node.js/TypeScript. It implements local JSON-based persistence (`/data/db.json`) allowing real-time administrative edits to persist securely across system restarts with zero third-party dependencies.\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\216\250 Visual & Interaction Design Concept\nAdhering strictly to **Light/Airy Minimalism**, the interface relies on precise typography and structural negative space:\n* **Off-White Canvas**: The layout sits on an eye-safe, cold light background with elegant charcoal-graphite copy (no harsh high-contrast pure black), framed by thin slate borders.\n* **Typographic Brand**: Headings pair tight-tracked, geometric **Plus Jakarta Sans** with tabular **JetBrains Mono** for numbers, countdowns, and session times.\n* **Interactive Hover States**: Speaker cards start in deep grayscale, blooming into saturated, college-specific brand colors on hover. Expandable timeline modules highlight related advisor cards.\n* **Dynamic Feedback**: Registration forms support smooth animations representing idle inputs, loading states, success screens, or error banners.\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\232\200 Functional Modules Implemented\n\n#### 1. Public Multi-Language Portal (RU / EN)\n* **Interactive Hero Banner**: Features an active live countdown timer tracking time left in days, hours, minutes, and seconds until the June 26th forum at the **Astana Technopark**.\n* **Key Metrics Grid**: Showcases key milestones\342\200\224500+ attendees cap, representative Ivy League admissions, and workshops.\n* **Speakers Grid (17 Consultants)**: Seeded with Kazakh students who secured admission to Harvard, Stanford, Oxford, Cambridge, and Nazarbayev University. Cards open a detailed modal containing their application bios, scores, and application tips.\n* **Chronological Timeline**: An accordion-expanding schedule coordinating times, panels, and academic topics, with clickable shortcut links to and from the advisor cards.\n* **Registration Ticket Passes**: Compiles Standard, Business, and VIP tiers. Button anchors automatically gather, serialize, and append administrative **UTM tracking metrics** (`utm_source`, `utm_medium`, `utm_campaign`) for proper sales attribution.\n* **horizontal Partners Wall**: Organizes sponsors by tiers (General Host, Academic Language Sponsors, and Information Partners).\n\n#### 2. Secure Administrative CMS Panel\n* **Protected Portal Entrance**: Admin session authorization is protected by password validation (default is set to **`admin`**).\n* **Content Operations (CRUD)**:\n  * **Presenters**: Update topics, graduation years, bio stories, gradients, or remove speakers.\n  * **Schedule Slots**: Add new events, assign times, or map speakers to schedules.\n  * **Partners/Sponsors**: Manage roles and sponsorship status.\n  * **Ticketing & UTMs**: Coordinate direct ticket pricing and tracking parameters in real time.\n  * **Event Settings**: Safely change the organizer contact email, phone, location, and the administrative password.\n* **Mailing List Spreadsheet**: Presents subscribers\' metadata (Names, Emails, Phones, with UTC timestamps) in an intuitive layout.\n* **Direct database Export**: Includes a custom CSV export stream. Clicking the button compiles and downloads the subscriber database as a `.csv` file directly.\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 1
      nanos: 402487935
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
