  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Clean Minimalism\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Clean Minimalism\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#F8FAFC] text-[#0F172A] font-sans flex flex-col overflow-hidden select-none\\\">\\n  <!-- Top Navigation / Header -->\\n  <header class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-10 h-24 border-b border-[#E2E8F0]\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-baseline gap-2\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter uppercase\\\">Global Edu Forum</span>\\n      <span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#3B82F6] rounded-full\\\"></span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-12 text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-[#3B82F6] transition-colors\\\">Speakers</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-[#3B82F6] transition-colors\\\">Schedule</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-[#3B82F6] transition-colors\\\">Partners</a>\\n      <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-[#0F172A] text-white hover:bg-[#3B82F6] transition-all\\\">\\n        Register Now\\n      </button>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <!-- Left Column: Hero & Meta -->\\n    <section class=\\\"w-[60%] border-r border-[#E2E8F0] flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"p-12 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white border border-[#E2E8F0] shadow-sm\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse\\\"></span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold opacity-70\\\">June 26, 2024 \342\200\242 Technopark Campus</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-[84px] leading-[0.9] font-black tracking-tight mb-8\\\">\\n          THE FUTURE OF<br/><span class=\\\"text-[#3B82F6]\\\">LEARNING.</span>\\n        </h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-lg text-[#475569] max-w-md leading-relaxed\\\">\\n          An exclusive gathering of 500 visionaries featuring 16+ speakers from the world\'s most prestigious universities and tech hubs.\\n        </p>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <!-- Stats Row -->\\n      <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 border-t border-[#E2E8F0] h-32\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center px-12 border-r border-[#E2E8F0]\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-2xl font-black\\\">16+</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50\\\">Global Speakers</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center px-12 border-r border-[#E2E8F0]\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-2xl font-black\\\">500</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50\\\">Attendees</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center px-12 bg-white\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-2xl font-black\\\">08</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50\\\">Hours of Networking</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n\\n    <!-- Right Column: Speakers & Preview -->\\n    <section class=\\\"w-[40%] flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"p-10 flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 flex justify-between items-center\\\">\\n          <span>Keynote Speakers</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[#3B82F6] cursor-pointer\\\">View All \342\206\222</span>\\n        </h3>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n          <!-- Speaker 1 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"group flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-20 h-20 bg-[#E2E8F0] rounded-lg grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all\\\"></div>\\n            <div>\\n              <h4 class=\\\"text-base font-bold\\\">Dr. Aris Thorne</h4>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#64748B]\\\">Director of AI, Stanford University</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"inline-block mt-2 text-[10px] font-bold text-[#3B82F6] uppercase\\\">09:30 AM \342\200\242 Main Hall</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          \\n          <!-- Speaker 2 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"group flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-20 h-20 bg-[#E2E8F0] rounded-lg grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all\\\"></div>\\n            <div>\\n              <h4 class=\\\"text-base font-bold\\\">Sarah J. Jenkins</h4>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#64748B]\\\">Innovation Lead at MIT Media Lab</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"inline-block mt-2 text-[10px] font-bold text-[#3B82F6] uppercase\\\">11:00 AM \342\200\242 Lab 01</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- Speaker 3 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"group flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-20 h-20 bg-[#E2E8F0] rounded-lg grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all\\\"></div>\\n            <div>\\n              <h4 class=\\\"text-base font-bold\\\">Prof. Kenzo Sato</h4>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#64748B]\\\">Quantum Computing, Oxford</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"inline-block mt-2 text-[10px] font-bold text-[#3B82F6] uppercase\\\">02:15 PM \342\200\242 Tech Stage</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Small Marquee/Partners at Bottom -->\\n      <div class=\\\"h-20 bg-[#F1F5F9] border-t border-[#E2E8F0] flex items-center px-10 gap-8\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 whitespace-nowrap\\\">Forum Partners</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-8 opacity-20 grayscale grayscale-100\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-black\\\">HARVARD</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-black\\\">TECHPARK</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-black\\\">GENIUS_CO</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-black\\\">FUTURE_ED</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Sub-footer / Legal -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"h-16 border-t border-[#E2E8F0] flex items-center justify-between px-10 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-[0.2em] opacity-40\\\">\\n    <span>\302\251 2024 Global Education Forum</span>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\">Privacy Policy</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\">Terms of Access</a>\\n    </div>\\n    <span>Design by ArchitectureStudio</span>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Clean Minimalism\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Clean Minimalism\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#F8FAFC] text-[#0F172A] font-sans flex flex-col overflow-hidden select-none\\\">\\n  <!-- Top Navigation / Header -->\\n  <header class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-10 h-24 border-b border-[#E2E8F0]\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-baseline gap-2\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter uppercase\\\">Global Edu Forum</span>\\n      <span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#3B82F6] rounded-full\\\"></span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-12 text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-[#3B82F6] transition-colors\\\">Speakers</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-[#3B82F6] transition-colors\\\">Schedule</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-[#3B82F6] transition-colors\\\">Partners</a>\\n      <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2.5 bg-[#0F172A] text-white hover:bg-[#3B82F6] transition-all\\\">\\n        Register Now\\n      </button>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <!-- Left Column: Hero & Meta -->\\n    <section class=\\\"w-[60%] border-r border-[#E2E8F0] flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"p-12 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white border border-[#E2E8F0] shadow-sm\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse\\\"></span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold opacity-70\\\">June 26, 2024 \342\200\242 Technopark Campus</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-[84px] leading-[0.9] font-black tracking-tight mb-8\\\">\\n          THE FUTURE OF<br/><span class=\\\"text-[#3B82F6]\\\">LEARNING.</span>\\n        </h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-lg text-[#475569] max-w-md leading-relaxed\\\">\\n          An exclusive gathering of 500 visionaries featuring 16+ speakers from the world\'s most prestigious universities and tech hubs.\\n        </p>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <!-- Stats Row -->\\n      <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 border-t border-[#E2E8F0] h-32\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center px-12 border-r border-[#E2E8F0]\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-2xl font-black\\\">16+</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50\\\">Global Speakers</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center px-12 border-r border-[#E2E8F0]\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-2xl font-black\\\">500</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50\\\">Attendees</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex flex-col justify-center px-12 bg-white\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-2xl font-black\\\">08</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50\\\">Hours of Networking</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n\\n    <!-- Right Column: Speakers & Preview -->\\n    <section class=\\\"w-[40%] flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"p-10 flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 flex justify-between items-center\\\">\\n          <span>Keynote Speakers</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[#3B82F6] cursor-pointer\\\">View All \342\206\222</span>\\n        </h3>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n          <!-- Speaker 1 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"group flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-20 h-20 bg-[#E2E8F0] rounded-lg grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all\\\"></div>\\n            <div>\\n              <h4 class=\\\"text-base font-bold\\\">Dr. Aris Thorne</h4>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#64748B]\\\">Director of AI, Stanford University</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"inline-block mt-2 text-[10px] font-bold text-[#3B82F6] uppercase\\\">09:30 AM \342\200\242 Main Hall</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          \\n          <!-- Speaker 2 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"group flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-20 h-20 bg-[#E2E8F0] rounded-lg grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all\\\"></div>\\n            <div>\\n              <h4 class=\\\"text-base font-bold\\\">Sarah J. Jenkins</h4>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#64748B]\\\">Innovation Lead at MIT Media Lab</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"inline-block mt-2 text-[10px] font-bold text-[#3B82F6] uppercase\\\">11:00 AM \342\200\242 Lab 01</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- Speaker 3 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"group flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-20 h-20 bg-[#E2E8F0] rounded-lg grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all\\\"></div>\\n            <div>\\n              <h4 class=\\\"text-base font-bold\\\">Prof. Kenzo Sato</h4>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#64748B]\\\">Quantum Computing, Oxford</p>\\n              <span class=\\\"inline-block mt-2 text-[10px] font-bold text-[#3B82F6] uppercase\\\">02:15 PM \342\200\242 Tech Stage</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Small Marquee/Partners at Bottom -->\\n      <div class=\\\"h-20 bg-[#F1F5F9] border-t border-[#E2E8F0] flex items-center px-10 gap-8\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 whitespace-nowrap\\\">Forum Partners</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-8 opacity-20 grayscale grayscale-100\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-black\\\">HARVARD</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-black\\\">TECHPARK</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-black\\\">GENIUS_CO</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-black\\\">FUTURE_ED</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Sub-footer / Legal -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"h-16 border-t border-[#E2E8F0] flex items-center justify-between px-10 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-[0.2em] opacity-40\\\">\\