g language-specific text and appropriate styles to align with the Clean Minimalism theme. I\'m using a responsive grid layout.\n\n\n**Evaluating CTA Buttons**\n\nI\'ve just evaluated the CTA buttons in `/src/components/Hero.tsx`. I\'m happy with how they align with the \"Stats Row\" at the bottom of the Design HTML. I like the use of `motion.div` for animation, and now will check the use of the `rounded-full` class. I will assess if they maintain the clean minimalist design.\n\n\n"
