re highly readable. I\'ve styled the speaker\'s name with `text-xs font-black text-slate-800` for clear prominence, and university information at the bottom with a smaller, more subtle font size. The speaker bio button is also styled for a strong contrast using `bg-slate-900` with uppercase text for emphasis, with a sleek look that is both modern and accessible, with a strong emphasis on readability.\n\n\n"
