    modified_response: "I have fully aligned and implemented the **Clean Minimalism** design theme across all panels and screens of the application:\n\n### Designed Improvements\n\n*   **Interactive Agenda Timeline** (`SchedulePanel`):\n    *   Transitioned to flat, sharp, non-rounded outline cards with **JetBrains Mono** font markings.\n    *   Introduced clean, geometric square bullet nodes connected by a single neutral track.\n    *   Replaced high-saturation sky-blue fills with subtle desaturated slates and a refined theme blue accent.\n*   **Admission Passes & Seating** (`TicketsPanel`):\n    *   Designed highly structured outline boxes with zero border radiuses.\n    *   Formed modern geometric label headers and clean pricing markers.\n    *   Restyled action buttons with sharp borders, high-contrast states, and letter-spaced uppercase labels.\n*   **Admissions Intelligence Newsletter & Guide** (`Newsletter`):\n    *   Embedded a minimalist subscription box framed in soft light gray lines.\n    *   Refined input fields with modern square borders, integrated icons, and desaturated focus indicators.\n    *   Tailored warning/success indicators with elegant neutral overlays.\n*   **Brand Integrations & Ecosystem** (`PartnersPanel`):\n    *   Crafted high-performance host cards utilizing thin borders and minimal structural spacing.\n    *   Replayed partner badges with monochromatic, Swiss-style hashtag formats.\n*   **Footer Area Styling**:\n    *   Optimized visual pairings using **Plus Jakarta Sans** Display typography and letter-spaced metadata accents.\n    *   Styled interactive contact resources to smoothly highlight with the main blue theme color.\n\nThe application has been verified to parse, compilation completed without error, and all strict ESLint checks passed successfully!"
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
